## Additional Terms and Disclaimers for Financial Analysis Software

This software is designed for educational, research, and analytical purposes only. 
By using this software, you acknowledge and agree to the following terms:

### 1. Not Investment Advice
This tool does not constitute investment advice, financial advice, professional 
