- Data privacy and protection regulations

### 6. Model Limitations
This K-Nearest Neighbors approach has inherent limitations:
- Results depend heavily on the selection and quality of comparable companies
- Model assumptions may not reflect actual market conditions
- Risk adjustments are subjective and may not capture all relevant factors
- Machine learning models can produce unexpected or erroneous results

